### 简历 CRUD 接口测试
### 先通过 auth.http 登录获取 token，替换下方 {{token}}

@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxNzU1NTA5NjUwNDY3IiwiZW1haWwiOiJ4eWhAcXEuY29tIiwiZXhwIjoxNzc1Mzg5NDg3fQ.pKlQxDsDp7Md6eBIVYjFnXdcpcIxQQHtiB8XGPSOaec

### 创建简历
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "title": "ai phd candidate",
    "target_role": "ai phd candidate"
}

###

### 查询简历详情（含所有 section）
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/detail
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "id": 1
}

###

### 我的简历列表
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/list
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "page": 1,
    "page_size": 20
}

###

### 更新简历基础信息
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "id": 1,
    "title": "高级后端工程师简历",
    "target_role": "高级后端工程师"
}

###

### 保存 basic_info section
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/section/save
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "resume_id": 1,
    "section_type": "basic_info",
    "order_index": 0,
    "content": {
        "name": "张三",
        "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
        "phone": "13800138312",
        "location": "北京",
        "linkedin": "",
        "github": "github.com/zhangsan"
    }
}

###

### 保存 work_exp section
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/section/save
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "resume_id": 1,
    "section_type": "work_exp",
    "order_index": 2,
    "content": [
        {
            "company": "字节跳动",
            "title": "高级后端工程师",
            "start": "2022-03",
            "end": "2024-06",
            "description": "- 主导推荐系统重构，将 P99 延迟从 800ms 降至 200ms\n- 设计并落地分布式限流方案，日处理请求 2 亿次"
        }
    ]
}

###

### 删除 section
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/section/delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "resume_id": 1,
    "section_type": "projects"
}

###

### 模板列表
GET http://localhost:8312/resume/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 导出 PDF
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/export/pdf
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "resume_id": 1,
    "template_name": "default.html"
}

###

### 删除简历
POST http://localhost:8312/resume/delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "id": 1
}

###
